The acronym ATMOS - Assimilation of Technically Motivated Souls -is a true representation of what we are. The national techno-management fest of BITS Pilani, Hyderabad Campus has grown from pillar to pillar in strength since its inception in 2012. Spanning over 3 days from the 14th to 16th October, ATMOS brings to you a plethora of exciting contests, workshops, lectures and much more! Featuring Illusions and Paradox as the theme this year, we are looking to make this edition bigger and better than ever before. Even sky is not the limit!
